      <title>阿根廷官员称该国已偿还主权债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/argentina-official-says-country-made-payments-on-sovereign-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷在周四的最后期限之前向国际债券持有人支付了款项，这标志着总统哈维尔·米莱伊为恢复投资者对这个惯犯债务国的信心又迈出了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/argentina-official-says-country-made-payments-on-sovereign-debt</guid>
