    <item>
      <title>Vitol 和 Uniper 支付 1700 万英镑帮助英国维持电力供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/gas-plants-operators-raked-in-17-million-as-britain-froze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，两座燃气发电厂获得了数百万英镑的赔偿，以弥补风力发电供应下降和零度以下气温导致需求增加造成的短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/gas-plants-operators-raked-in-17-million-as-britain-froze</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:53:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银维持 2008 年高点，Kepler 预计 2027 年将回购 150 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/ubs-holds-2008-high-as-kepler-sees-15-billion-buyback-to-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 巩固了 2008 年高点的近期涨幅，因为 Kepler Cheuvreux SA 表示，该银行可以克服对更高资本要求的担忧，并在未来几年通过股票回购分配高达 150 亿美元的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/ubs-holds-2008-high-as-kepler-sees-15-billion-buyback-to-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:40:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗公司的泽尔特认为私人和公共市场壁垒正在消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/public-private-markets-barriers-to-fall-apollo-s-zelter-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司联席总裁詹姆斯泽尔特在接受彭博电视采访时表示，随着企业越来越多地受益于更广泛的融资选择，私人市场和公开市场之间的障碍正在减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/public-private-markets-barriers-to-fall-apollo-s-zelter-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国市场抛售加剧，英镑跌至年内最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pound-slumps-to-weakest-since-2023-amid-broad-uk-market-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心借贷成本飙升导致工党政府难以控制赤字，英镑跌至一年多来的最低点，股市下跌，英国政府债券连续第四天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pound-slumps-to-weakest-since-2023-amid-broad-uk-market-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 07:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
